title: Garmin Bluechart G2 Vision VEU014R - Italy, Adriatic Sea
description:
The new Garmin G2 charts don't go into MapSource only to Garmin Mobile PC, but to use the full potential (e.g. embedded photographic images) you have to use it on a GPS that supports G2 Vision BlueCharts.
BlueChart G2 Vision maps are only sold on SD cards!!!

VEU014R - Italy, Adriatic Sea


Includes all of the Adriatic Sea and extends south to Siracusa, Sicilia and Gulf of Arcadia, Greece. Includes detailed coverage of Lago Maggiore, Lago d'Iseo, and Lago d'Garda in Italy.

US List Price: $374.98
